		<item>
			<title>Lens, Aperture, &amp; Shutter Module</title>
			<link>https://pascoli.github.io/undergraduate-engineering/modular-camera/lens-aperture--shutter-2.html</link>
			<description>
				&lt;div class="article-summary"&gt;&lt;p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana;"&gt;The fabric on the back of the module allows for the smooth linear motion necessary for proper focusing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			</description>
			<pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2014 22:56:09 +0100</pubDate>
			<guid>https://pascoli.github.io/undergraduate-engineering/modular-camera/lens-aperture--shutter-2.html</guid>
