		<item>
			<title>Shutter Mechanism</title>
			<link>https://pascoli.github.io/undergraduate-engineering/modular-camera/shutter-mechanism.html</link>
			<description>
				&lt;div class="article-summary"&gt;&lt;p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana;"&gt;A solenoid pin, when triggered, fires the bristol leaf-blade downward and a torsion spring returns the blade to its original position.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			</description>
